Merged
public class Merged extends FeatureDeriveFromPair
Evaluates a feature on the merged object created from a pair of objects.

This class extends FeatureDeriveFromPair to specifically calculate a feature value for the merged object created from both objects in a pair.

Author:
Owen Feehan
